@startuml WebGPU_Frame_Flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceArrowColor #333333
skinparam participantBackgroundColor #E8F5E9
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFF9C4

title WebGPU Frame Execution Flow

participant "Application" as App #E1F5FE
participant "RenderGraph" as Graph #FFF3E0
participant "CommandEncoder" as Encoder #E8F5E9
participant "RenderPass" as Pass #E8F5E9
participant "Queue" as Queue #C8E6C9
participant "SwapChain" as Swap #BBDEFB
participant "GPU" as GPU #FFCDD2

== Frame N ==

App -> App: Update(deltaTime)
note right: Game logic,\nPhysics,\nAnimations

App -> Graph: BuildRenderGraph()
note right: Define passes\nand dependencies

App -> Graph: SetFrameData()
note left: View/Proj matrices,\nLights, Objects

Graph -> Graph: Compile()
note right: Optimize pass order,\nAllocate resources

App -> Swap: GetCurrentTextureView()
note right: Acquire next\nswapchain image

Graph -> Encoder: CreateCommandEncoder()

loop For each RenderPass
    Graph -> Pass: Execute(encoder)
    
    Pass -> Encoder: BeginRenderPass(descriptor)
    note right: Color attachments,\nDepth attachment,\nLoad/Store ops
    
    Pass -> Pass: SetPipeline()
    Pass -> Pass: SetBindGroups()
    
    loop For each DrawCall
        Pass -> Pass: SetVertexBuffer()
        Pass -> Pass: SetIndexBuffer()
        Pass -> Pass: Draw() or DrawIndexed()
    end
    
    Pass -> Encoder: EndRenderPass()
end

Graph -> Encoder: Finish()
note right: Returns\nCommandBuffer

Graph -> Queue: Submit(commandBuffer)
note left: Send to GPU

Queue -> GPU: Execute Commands
note right: Async execution

App -> Swap: Present()
note left: Display frame

== Frame N+1 (Parallel) ==

App -> App: Update(deltaTime)
note right: CPU prepares\nnext frame while\nGPU renders

GPU --> Queue: Signal completion
note left: Via callback

@enduml